-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/c6fe7a4c-01c6-406f-afa4-771fbe937256/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/david.png" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" width="346" height="345" natural-width="346" natural-height="345"></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-lg-9 gf_col-md-9 gf_col-xs-8" id="c-1666609744580" data-id="1666609744580" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1666609918984" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1666609918984"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Hi ‚Äì&nbsp;<span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.3px; font-style: var(--font-body-style);"><span style="color: inherit;">I'm </span><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/deividas-kovger-125895188/" class="" style=""><strong style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38);">David, the Founder & CEO of Monkeflow</strong></a><span style="color: inherit;">. I've&nbsp; sent over 600m emails and done $25M just in email revenue for eCommerce clients alone.</span></span></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1666610163874" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1666610163874" style=""><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1666610163825" data-id="1666610163825"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1666610156907" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1666610156907" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p></p><p></p><p></p><p>Yet, there was this one thing I've noticed after&nbsp;<strong style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.3px; font-style: var(--font-body-style);">auditing 125 email Klaviyo accounts.&nbsp;</strong><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.3px; font-style: var(--font-body-style);">95% of eCommerce stores were leaving </span><i style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.3px;">so much money on the table.&nbsp;</i><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.3px; font-style: var(--font-body-style);">Even those, that had email marketing agencies working with them.</span></p><p><br></p><p>We have accounts making<strong> $50M/year with 50% of whole store's revenue </strong>coming just from email & SMS.&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.3px; font-style: var(--font-body-style);">That's </span><strong style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.3px; font-style: var(--font-body-style);">$25M per year coming just from email & SMS alone</strong><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.3px; font-style: var(--font-body-style);">. Just imagine the impact.</span></p><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.3px; font-style: var(--font-body-style);"><br></span></p><p>The key ‚Äì sending newsletters&nbsp;<span style="font-weight: bold;"><i>consistently.</i></span></p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1678708109064" class="elemen